quran[9{c,v,t}:
34,49,Qul jaaa'al haqqu wa maa yubdi'ul baatilu wa maa yu'eed
34,50,Qul in dalaltu fainnamaaa adillu 'alaa nafsee wa inih-tadaitu fabimaa yoohee ilaiya Rabbee; innahoo Samee'un Qareeb
34,51,Wa law taraaa iz fazi'oo falaa fawta wa ukhizoo mim makaanin qareeb
34,52,Wa qaloo aamannaa bihee wa annaa lahumut tanaawushu mim makaanim ba'eed
34,53,Wa qad kafaroo bihee min qablu wa yaqzifoona bilghaibi mim makaanim ba'eed
34,54,Wa heela bainahum wa baina maa yashtahoona kamaa fu'ila bi-ashyaa'ihim min qabl; innahum kaanoo fee shakkim mureeb (section 6)
35,1,Alhamdu lillaahi faatiris samaawaati wal ardi jaa'ilil malaaa'ikati rusulan uleee ajnihatim masnaa wa sulaasa wa rubaa'; yazeedu fil khalqi maa yashaaa'; innal laaha 'alaa kulli shai'in Qadeer
35,2,Maa yaftahil laahu linnaaasi mir rahmatin falaa mumsika lahaa wa maa yumsik falaa mursila lahoo mimb'dih; wa Huwal 'Azeezul Hakeem
35,3,Yaaa ayyuhan naasuzkuroo ni'matal laahi 'alaikum; hal min khaaliqin ghairul laahi yarzuqukum minas samaaa'i wal ard; laaa ilaaha illaa Huwa fa annaa tu'fakoon
